inc::latest::private(3) User Contributed Perl Documentation inc::latest::private(3)

NAME

inc::latest::private - private implementation for inc::latest

VERSION

version 0.500

DESCRIPTION

This module has the private methods used to find and load bundled modules. It should not be used directly.
